<div class="modal modal--medium" id="modal1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="#modal1Title">
    <div class="modal__dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal__content">
            <div class="modal__header">
                <div class="modal__title" id="modal1Title">콘텐츠 완료하기</div>
                <button type="button" class="ic-button" data-dialog-close aria-label="팝업닫기">
                    <i class="ic ic-close" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal__body">
                <div class="form">
                    <div class="fields">
                        <div class="field">
                            <label class="dpb medium ft14">제목</label>
                            <textarea class="textarea textarea--tiny" maxlength="50" placeholder="원하시는 콘텐츠 제목을 입력해주세요. 입력하지 않아도 오늘 날짜로 저장돼요"></textarea>
                            <div class="textarea__lengths">
                                <label class="error" aria-hidden="true">입력 가능한 글자수를 초과했어요. 안정적인 교정을 위해 글자수를 조정해주세요.</label>
                                <div class="textarea__lengths__box">
                                    <span class="textarea__lengths--current">0</span>/ <span class="textarea__lengths--total">50</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="info">
                    <i class="ic ic-exclamation" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    <p class="text">작성하신 콘텐츠는 마이페이지로 이동합니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal__footer">
                <button type="button" class="button pw100">완료하기</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>